title: Imani Smith, Former ‘Lion King’ Broadway Actress, Dies in Alleged Homicide at 26
summary: "Imani had her whole life ahead of her. She was a vivacious, loving and fiercely talented person," Smith's aunt, Kira Helper, wrote on GoFundMe.

title: Matt Rogers on His Christmas Tour, the State of Hollywood and His Unexpected Next Podcast Idea
summary: The 35-year-old actor, comedian, musician and podcaster says he’s finally starting to learn his professional bandwidth after years of dabbling in several sectors of the industry: “I think we all lie to ourselves a little bit about what we can and can't handle.”
